{"tid":52544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"優先𨋢？ 港鐵我屌你老母啊","createTime":"2016-12-24T07:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T09:57:50.000Z","uid":6653,"like":0,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9aeca0804edd35c906dcbe12d2164a2c0e24f52","tid":52544,"uid":6653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/09i69wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F09i69wf.jpg&h=1d006ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱家駿攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/150445_55509465d621cf79db4575d5594d03f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F150445_55509465d621cf79db4575d5594d03f7.jpg&h=53cd7ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱家駿攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/150459_f3b3d7f31a82e970bb062cbeb2cd017c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F150459_f3b3d7f31a82e970bb062cbeb2cd017c.jpg&h=7d5f0d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱家駿攝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47y573Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47y573Z.jpg&h=24654263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵優先座問題已甚惹爭議，今次南港鐵綫通車，港鐵更新引入「優先𨋢」，車站內前往大堂的電梯全部貼上紅色優先使用貼紙，供有需要人士優先使用。港鐵車務營運總管李聖基指，由於車站有多條扶手梯前往各層，因而考慮引入優先使用電梯方便有需要人士使用。<br />\n<br />\n李聖基又指，金鐘站現有荃灣綫及港島綫月台的擴建位置，今日雖仍落下防火閘及以膠布圍封，主要是因有關位置可通往擴建部分，需要在周三南港島綫通車時同步啟用。他又強調，車站工程經已全部完成，可於通車日全部啟用。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早前南港島綫列車在測試期間曾經死機，李強調列車所有大問題已處理，目前尚餘輕微調較作正進行，如令列車停站更準確。他又指，南港島綫車站始終按中型鐵路規模設計，會密切留意人流問題，各站會有人流管制措施對應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚野優先𨋢呀 整多條線叫優先線關愛線呀笨 屌你老母臭化閪垃圾港鐵</span></span>"},{"pid":"85ffc6de15bcfd0c0d8c3be81a65a9c035b6c86b","tid":52544,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"照入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd1da48fbaad8b6740d20d3bf33405293b5b82c","tid":52544,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"走火入魔"},{"pid":"39e870ac715a4c72e1042f1edd3215950907d464","tid":52544,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:18:46.000Z","msg":"屌7班廢老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a54d1b15e5adf4a216474b9aa9b23fb8713566","tid":52544,"uid":34229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"照搭  屌尻班廢老"},{"pid":"4bf9947652927cd81f99d78a9012cab109f834fd","tid":52544,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"坦白講句<br />\n不嬲都搭扶手電梯<br />\n關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"44003396897930bbd705b5b0b9b3ebc59df8923f","tid":52544,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"優先空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724b92e24dd08146d44c4de37e4bd7741078b195","tid":52544,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老味 呢家咩都有優先"},{"pid":"909a5181280bf5bed0984d5a8bce190762753bb1","tid":52544,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"廢老先會搭"},{"pid":"a130aa9a3b5c3a993f13e6cae964046a218ce7d2","tid":52544,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0256e73a306f8028dd2a75c5fff1875fffc99fd","tid":52544,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<br />\n照搭"},{"pid":"73e9ec7f6