ces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1378ecc2e26c92218d56878cc88acf7334af483","tid":52544,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"繼續分化"},{"pid":"aa0ecb1501fb661821d16933d4a20163dbbe036f","tid":52544,"uid":58643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>優先𨋢=俾d廢老唔好阻鳩住條扶手梯左邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得啱，啲廢老去曬搭優先𨋢，條扶手電梯鬆動曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd4d58bdd1d3c79e9d2844eb4862dca65ee25d4","tid":52544,"uid":37069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時先至有優先骨灰龕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英年早逝要罰款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ed394fa633928640ad7267baf264c766c7fe5d","tid":52544,"uid":29697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"根本而家啲𨋢係俾啲行得走得的廢老都唔俾有需要的人搭，仲有啲大大件行李的支那人<br />\n啲廢老入到𨋢企哂路中心，後面有輪椅有bb車都俾佢地阻著唔撚入到<br />\n仲要唔撚排隊，成日係側邊打尖入𨋢<br />\n<br />\n利申：死廢青，冇得唔搭𨋢"},{"pid":"42753d80be6f50426e34bdddffda483e8ab904fb","tid":52544,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"雖然平時唔搭港鐵部𨋢但諗落都on9"},{"pid":"fa59e0e19a23fe65dae7d1dcd87f69e5d5e13d45","tid":52544,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"真心覺得個社會惡意灌輸優先文化<br />\n香港一直行緊都係公平原則<br />\n愈多愈多野都搞優先,姐係俾大條道理人地打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54fd955d818d7da69f53ec9d4c3f756c2032451","tid":52544,"uid":29592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:23:05.000Z","msg":"優先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b9e921d065ff62eb3edc1eb310117b64d89aeb","tid":52544,"uid":56245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep